dct_title_s: Rand, McNally & Co.'s indexed atlas of the world map of South America
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Includes inset map of the Galapagos Islands. Running title in margin: Rand, McNally & Company's indexed atlas of the world. Text on verso: Continent of South America.
